data.enText: making you want to do, try, taste, etc. sth

simple_means.memory_skill: invite 邀请 + ing 正…的，使人…的 → 诱人的

value.def: If you say that something is inviting, you mean that it has good qualities that attract you or make you want to experience it.

example.ex: The February air was soft, cool, and inviting...
example.tran: 二月的空气柔和、凉爽而怡人。

example.ex: There is an inviting restaurant with an outdoor terrace.
example.tran: 有一家诱人的带露天阳台的饭馆。

example.ex: The waters of the tropics are invitingly clear.
